{
  "text": "About 50 % of women with circulating auto-antibodies who have children with NLE are asymptomatic, and some of them will develop some kind of rheumatologic disease, particularly Sjögren Syndrome, SLE and less often mixed connective tissue diseases [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "22311481"
